name: Fnf silver banana edition: EXTREMELY EARLY DEMO
name_original: Fnf silver banana edition: EXTREMELY EARLY DEMO
description: This is just a super early sneak peak of the fnf mod I'm working on right now. As of right now, nothing is permanent. Once I get a hang of using Fl studio, I'll change up the songs, and maybe even start using mine-imator instead of Paint 3d. I want to start working more on my Baldi mods and getting those published, because that is what more of my fnf content is going to be about anyway. The only reason I got started on this mod was because Dave and Bambi Is really popular, and that I'm a part of the community as well. So just to be clear, anything in this fnf mod so far is subject to change so please tell me if there are any bugs. By the way, I did not voice Jayden.
